::Mosquitor/Zeus::

Mosquitor is thrown backwards as another one of Zeus' thunderbolts 
hits him, slamming into the tree on which Set and Scourge are 
fighting.

Zeus notices Scourge on the tree and his eyes narrow. Taking careful 
aim, he fires at the middle of Scourge's back right before Mosquitor 
tackles him (Zeus).
